#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga"
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Dīghalaṭṭhisutta"
msgstr "13. With Dīghalaṭṭhi"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.13:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn2.13:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

msgctxt "sn2.13:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho dīghalaṭṭhi devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo "
"kevalakappaṃ veḷuvanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, the glorious god Dīghalaṭṭhi, lighting up the entire "
"Bamboo Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side,"

msgctxt "sn2.13:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho dīghalaṭṭhi devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ "
"abhāsi:"
msgstr "and recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.120"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.1"
msgid "“Bhikkhu siyā jhāyī vimuttacitto,"
msgstr "“Suppose a mendicant is one who practices absorption, freed in mind."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.2"
msgid "Ākaṅkhe ce hadayassānupattiṃ;"
msgstr "If they want to reach the heart’s peace,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.3"
msgid "Lokassa ñatvā udayabbayañca,"
msgstr "having known the arising and passing of the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.4"
msgid "Sucetaso anissito tadānisaṃso”ti."
msgstr "healthy-minded, independent, that is their reward.”"
